sj1 = StringJoiner()
sj1.add_multi('e1', 'e2', 'e3')
sj2 = StringJoiner()
sj2.add_multi('e2', 'e3', 'e4')
sj1_2 = sj1 - sj2
self.assertEqual('e1', str(sj1_2))
expected__repr__ = (
    '{"separator": ",", "prefix": "", "suffix": "", "nelem": 1, "str_length": 2, "elements": ["e1"]}'
    )
self.assertEqual(expected__repr__, repr(sj1_2))
sj2_1 = sj2 - sj1
self.assertEqual('e4', str(sj2_1))
expected__repr__ = (
    '{"separator": ",", "prefix": "", "suffix": "", "nelem": 1, "str_length": 2, "elements": ["e4"]}'
    )
self.assertEqual(expected__repr__, repr(sj2_1))
